#NAME
#
#  This program is based on the calculations of the AMOC but will actually
#  calculate ocean heat transport for the Global, Atlantic, Pacific and Indian
#  oceans
#
#  For the atlantic and the Pacific there may be some inflow through the CAS
#  so account for this.
#
#  Southward transport is that flowing from north + that coming from the CAS
#
#  it will write all the OHT out to a file.
#
#  The heat transport equation is back to being
#  rho * cp * v * theta  (as we no longer need a reference temperaturet
#
#

